text: Night of the Kings () is a 2020 Ivorian French Canadian Senegalese fantasy drama movie directed by Philippe Lacôte and starring Koné Bakary, Isaka Sawadogo, Steve Tientcheu, Laetitia Ky, Denis Lavant. ==Other websites== * * Koné Bakary’s Road to the Oscars, TheWrap, January 14, 2021 Category:2020 drama movies Category:2020 fantasy movies Category:Ivorian movies Category:French fantasy movies Category:French drama movies Category:Canadian fantasy movies Category:Canadian drama movies Category:Senegalese movies
